title: Shin Jung Hyun and the Men - It's A Lie (1972/2000) [FLAC]
description:
Artist: Shin Jung Hyun and the Men
Album: It's A Lie
Year: 1972/2000
Country: South Korea
Genre: Psychedelic Rock
No Artwork

A great psychedelic album with 3 long tracks and very good guitar and organ work
'the Collection of Korean psych's golden age'. This album contains the peak of the 70's psychedelia of Korea.

Tracklist:

1 Beautiful Country 9:56
2 It's A Lie 22:15
3 A Woman In The Mist 11:32
